title: Geroge Ezra - BBC Radio 1 Big Weekend [Video Album]
description:
BBC's Radio 1 Biggest Weekend is the replacement for the Glastonbury Festival which is taking a year or two out to allow the ground to recover in the Farm which is used for this every year.  Held in Venues in all four member states of the UK it not only showcases the best of British but World music as well.

If the group were touring the UK that weekend you can expect to see them somewhere.

My thanks to the original seeder of the concert stream and of course BBC Music for this wonderful celebration of Music to help forget the mistakes of Trump and Brexit.
